statements.sql: select count(*) as aggregate from `activity_log` where ((`activity_log`.`subject_type` = 'Modules\Edu\Entities\Comment' and exists (select * from `edu_comment` where `activity_log`.`subject_id` = `edu_comment`.`id`)) or (`activity_log`.`subject_type` = 'Modules\Edu\Entities\Lesson' and exists (select * from `edu_lessons` where `activity_log`.`subject_id` = `edu_lessons`.`id`)) or (`activity_log`.`subject_type` = 'Modules\Edu\Entities\Sign' and exists (select * from `edu_sign` where `activity_log`.`subject_id` = `edu_sign`.`id`)) or (`activity_log`.`subject_type` = 'Modules\Edu\Entities\Topic' and exists (select * from `edu_topic` where `activity_log`.`subject_id` = `edu_topic`.`id`))) and `site_id` = 1

select * from `activity_log` where ((`activity_log`.`subject_type` = 'Modules\Edu\Entities\Comment' and exists (select * from `edu_comment` where `activity_log`.`subject_id` = `edu_comment`.`id`)) or (`activity_log`.`subject_type` = 'Modules\Edu\Entities\Lesson' and exists (select * from `edu_lessons` where `activity_log`.`subject_id` = `edu_lessons`.`id`)) or (`activity_log`.`subject_type` = 'Modules\Edu\Entities\Sign' and exists (select * from `edu_sign` where `activity_log`.`subject_id` = `edu_sign`.`id`)) or (`activity_log`.`subject_type` = 'Modules\Edu\Entities\Topic' and exists (select * from `edu_topic` where `activity_log`.`subject_id` = `edu_topic`.`id`))) and `site_id` = 1 order by `id` desc limit 15 offset 0
